==== ENTRY 3 ====
HEADWORD: Avow
<hw>A*vow"</hw>, <pos>v. t. & i.</pos> <ety>[OF. <ets>avouer</ets>, fr.
LL. <ets>votare</ets> to vow, fr. L. <ets>votun</ets>. See
<er>Vote</er>, <pos>n.</pos>]</ety> <def>To bind, or to devote, by a
vow.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Wyclif.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Avow</ent>⟦br⟧

